artifacts.summary: Analysis of contrapositive approach to TruthLemma backward direction - concludes the approach does not resolve the omega-rule limitation

findings.reason: While mathematically equivalent, contrapositive still requires witness extraction from MCS which is not possible
findings.reason_depth: Bounded time domain changes semantics and has compositionality issues
findings.recommendation: Accept current forward-only truth lemma design - completeness proofs are already sorry-free
